## Connects To
- SLAM Token (mint authority = presale program)
- USDC/USDT mints (payment tokens)
- Presale backend (off-chain indexer reads on-chain events)

## Git
- Remote: `https://github.com/nexus-ledger-blockchain/slam-presale-program.git`
- Branch: `master`

## Security Notes
- Program uses PDA for user allocation (no user-controlled seeds)
- All state mutations require signature checks
- Treasury withdrawal requires multisig (2-of-3)
- Contribution validation: min/max limits, round timing, payment token validation

## Testing Plan
1. Unit tests for each instruction (`tests/*.ts`)
2. Integration test: full presale flow (init → contribute → claim)
3. Edge cases: early contribution, late claim, partial vesting
4. Upgrade test: deploy v2, migrate state

